        "subject": "LU-511: Race condition loading modules causes mount to fail",
        "message": "LU-511: Race condition loading modules causes mount to fail\n\nOn servers with more than one OST, the module load on the initial\nboot intermittently fails. This patch tries to load lustre modules\nbefore actually starting lustre targets. See Oracle bug 24464.\n\nChange-Id: Idc68181bf956dd75e5a932164716acb2a0c78ef1\nSigned-off-by: Wally Wang <wang@cray.com>\n"
